On the countertops, there are various items including cardboard boxes, paper bags, folded clothing, and some papers. A white stool with a chrome base is positioned on the right side of the room. A single dome light fixture is mounted on the ceiling. The photo is taken from a doorway, with the door frame visible on the right.
